# Filament v5 Conventions

Panel: `admin` at `/admin` ‚Äî configured only in `AdminPanelProvider` (no `config/filament.php`).

## Resource layout (required)

```
app/Filament/Resources/{Plural}/
  {Singular}Resource.php
  Schemas/{Singular}Form.php      # Form::configure(Schema $schema)
  Tables/{Plural}Table.php        # Table::configure(Table $table)
  Pages/List|Create|Edit{...}.php
```

Use Filament `Schema` for forms (v5), not legacy Form API. Prefer native Form/Table builders over custom Blade.

## Navigation

- Groups: **Finances** (Invoices, Budgets), **Settings** (Labels)
- Theme: amber/zinc, Outfit font, SPA mode, collapsible sidebar, database notifications
- Breadcrumbs: disabled panel-wide via `->breadcrumbs(false)` in `AdminPanelProvider` ‚Äî do not re-enable per resource
- Custom pages: `Dashboard`, `ReceiptUploadPage`, `Auth/EditProfile`

## Widgets

Dashboard widgets live in `app/Filament/Widgets/`. Month filtering uses `InteractsWithDashboardMonth` + `DashboardMonthAnalytics` / `DashboardMonthPeriod`.

## Prefer

- `relationship()` for related selects
- Notifications on user-facing actions
- Soft-delete aware queries (`withoutGlobalScopes` on record binding when needed)
- Icon-only row actions (View/Edit/Delete): set globally in `AppServiceProvider` via `Table::configureUsing` ‚Üí `modifyUngroupedRecordActionsUsing(fn (Action $action) => $action->iconButton())` ‚Äî do not re-add visible labels per table
- `created_at` (and similar upload timestamps) use `->since()->dateTimeTooltip()` ‚Äî relative time in the cell, full date/time on hover (same as Receipt Upload ‚ÄúUploaded At‚Äù)

## View records (required)

Always use slide-over view ‚Äî never add a dedicated `ViewRecord` / `View{Model}` page.

- Resource tables: `ViewAction::make()->slideOver()` in `recordActions` (before Edit/Delete)
- Notification / deep-link ‚ÄúView‚Äù CTAs: open the resource list with Filament table-action query params so the same slide-over mounts:

```php
Resource::getUrl('index', [
    'tableAction' => 'view',
    'tableActionRecord' => $record->getRouteKey(),
]);
```

## Avoid

- Custom Blade unless native components cannot do the job
- Putting business logic (Ollama, Drive sync, alerts) inside Resource classes ‚Äî call Services/Jobs
- Dedicated View pages (`ViewRecord`, `make:filament-page --type=ViewRecord`, `getPages()` `view` routes)
- Omitting View from resource table `recordActions`
- Visible text labels on ungrouped table record actions (icons only; tooltips/a11y labels remain)
- Raw `->dateTime()` alone on `created_at` resource columns ‚Äî use `since()` + `dateTimeTooltip()` instead